FBIS3-56684 "drsov012_c_94041" FBIS-SOV-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 Federal Assembly Russia's Choice Against New Parliament Building Project MK1501105094 Moscow MOSKOVSKIY KOMSOMOLETS in Russian 15 Jan 94 p 2 MK1501105094 Moscow MOSKOVSKIY KOMSOMOLETS Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed untitled report under the "Round the Clock Nonstop" rubric] [Text] The Russia's Choice deputy faction is speaking against the construction of a new parliament building that would cost $588 million from state coffers. According to Russia's Choice, this sum is quite sufficient to take care of military conversion on a Russia- wide scale for one year.
